{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":1,"result":{"protocolVersion":"2024-11-05","capabilities":{"tools":{"listChanged":false}},"serverInfo":{"version":"1.0.0","name":"OpsGuard-MCP"},"instructions":"OpsGuard 运维工具服务端：感知/巡检类工具（annotations.readOnlyHint=true）为只读采集，可直接调用；变更类工具（annotations.readOnlyHint=false，如 log_rotate/service_restart/config_backup）内置安全闭环——每次调用先经意图风险护栏裁决（红线直接拒绝，confirm 也无法越过），需审批操作必须先获得 pendingMutationId，再携带 pendingMutationId + confirm=true 二次确认；真实执行前自动备份目标文件并登记回滚账本（POST /api/ops/rollback/{traceId} 一键回滚），全程按 traceId 溯源审计；默认 dry-run 演示模式不真实落盘变更。"}}
{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":2,"result":{"tools":[{"name":"config_backup","description":"【变更类·非破坏】为指定配置文件创建带时间戳的备份副本（<path>.bak-<时间戳>），真实执行时受管备份目录同步留存快照并登记回滚账本（可一键恢复）。与其他变更工具共用护栏裁决与 pendingMutationId + confirm=true 二次确认门禁；默认 dry-run","inputSchema":{"type":"object","properties":{"path":{"type":"string","description":"待备份配置文件的绝对路径，如 /etc/nginx/nginx.conf、/etc/my.cnf"},"confirm":{"type":"boolean","description":"二次确认标志：首次调用返回风险裁决（REVIEW_PENDING），审阅后需同时携带 pendingMutationId 才会执行","default":false},"pendingMutationId":{"type":"string","description":"首次 REVIEW_PENDING 返回的待确认变更 id；confirm=true 时必须携带且与同一工具/参数匹配"}},"required":["path"],"additionalProperties":false},"annotations":{"title":"config_backup","readOnlyHint":false,"destructiveHint":false,"idempotentHint":false,"openWorldHint":false}},{"name":"db_sense","description":"采集数据库运行状态（免凭据只读探测）：服务进程(ps)、监听端口(ss)与已建立连接数，支持 MySQL/PostgreSQL/Redis；可选 engine 指定引擎（默认 auto 全部探测），目标机未部署对应数据库时优雅降级","inputSchema":{"type":"object","properties":{"engine":{"type":"string","description":"要探测的数据库引擎；auto 表示依次探测全部三种","enum":["auto","mysql","postgresql","redis"],"default":"auto"}},"additionalProperties":false},"annotations":{"title":"db_sense","readOnlyHint":true,"destructiveHint":false,"idempotentHint":true,"openWorldHint":false}},{"name":"disk_sense","description":"采集磁盘信息：各文件系统使用率(df)与指定目录占用(du)；可选 path 指定探查目录(默认 /var/log)","inputSchema":{"type":"object","properties":{"path":{"type":"string","description":"du 探查的绝对目录路径（非绝对路径将回退默认值）","pattern":"^/","default":"/var/log","examples":["/var/log","/data","/tmp","/home"]}},"additionalProperties":false},"annotations":{"title":"disk_sense","readOnlyHint":true,"destructiveHint":false,"idempotentHint":true,"openWorldHint":false}},{"name":"log_rotate","description":"【变更类】轮转指定日志文件：先复制归档为 <path>.<时间戳>，再将原文件截断为 0 字节释放磁盘。仅允许 /var/log/ 下或以 .log 结尾的文件。内置安全闭环：护栏风险裁决、pendingMutationId + confirm=true 二次确认、执行前自动备份、回滚账本登记；默认 dry-run 不真实落盘","inputSchema":{"type":"object","properties":{"path":{"type":"string","description":"待轮转日志文件的绝对路径，须位于 /var/log/ 下或以 .log 结尾，如 /var/log/nginx/access.log"},"confirm":{"type":"boolean","description":"二次确认标志：首次调用返回风险裁决（REVIEW_PENDING），审阅后需同时携带 pendingMutationId 才会执行","default":false},"pendingMutationId":{"type":"string","description":"首次 REVIEW_PENDING 返回的待确认变更 id；confirm=true 时必须携带且与同一工具/参数匹配"}},"required":["path"],"additionalProperties":false},"annotations":{"title":"log_rotate","readOnlyHint":false,"destructiveHint":true,"idempotentHint":false,"openWorldHint":false}},{"name":"log_sense","description":"采集日志信息：最近的错误级别 systemd 日志(journalctl -p err)；可选 unit 限定某个服务单元、lines 指定行数(默认 100)","inputSchema":{"type":"object","properties":{"unit":{"type":"string","description":"systemd 服务单元名；留空则采集全系统错误日志","examples":["nginx","sshd","mysqld","docker"]},"lines":{"type":"integer","description":"拉取的日志行数","minimum":1,"maximum":1000,"default":100}},"additionalProperties":false},"annotations":{"title":"log_sense","readOnlyHint":true,"destructiveHint":false,"idempotentHint":true,"openWorldHint":false}},{"name":"metrics_sense","description":"采集监控系统指标（Prometheus 文本格式）：source=node-exporter 抓取主机监控(默认 127.0.0.1:9100/metrics)，source=actuator 抓取本服务自监控(默认 127.0.0.1:8080/actuator/prometheus)；可选 filter 按指标名前缀过滤、lines 限制返回行数；端点不可达时优雅降级","inputSchema":{"type":"object","properties":{"source":{"type":"string","description":"指标来源：node-exporter=主机级监控（需目标机部署 node_exporter），actuator=本服务自监控端点","enum":["node-exporter","actuator"],"default":"node-exporter"},"port":{"type":"integer","description":"监控端点端口；缺省 node-exporter=9100、actuator=8080","minimum":1,"maximum":65535},"filter":{"type":"string","description":"指标名前缀过滤，如 node_load、node_memory、jvm_memory；留空返回全部（受 lines 限制）"},"lines":{"type":"integer","description":"最多返回的指标行数（注释行不计）","minimum":1,"maximum":500,"default":50}},"additionalProperties":false},"annotations":{"title":"metrics_sense","readOnlyHint":true,"destructiveHint":false,"idempotentHint":true,"openWorldHint":false}},{"name":"network_sense","description":"采集网络信息：监听中的端口及进程(ss -tnlp)、各状态连接统计(ss -s)；可选 port 只聚焦某个端口（监听方 + 已建立连接）","inputSchema":{"type":"object","properties":{"port":{"type":"integer","description":"只聚焦该端口：返回其监听进程与已建立连接；留空返回全量监听端口与统计","minimum":1,"maximum":65535}},"additionalProperties":false},"annotations":{"title":"network_sense","readOnlyHint":true,"destructiveHint":false,"idempotentHint":true,"openWorldHint":false}},{"name":"process_sense","description":"采集进程信息：按 CPU 占用排序的进程列表，含状态列以识别僵尸进程；可选 limit 只取前 N 个进程","inputSchema":{"type":"object","properties":{"limit":{"type":"integer","description":"只返回 CPU 占用前 N 个进程；留空或 0 返回全部","minimum":0,"maximum":200,"default":0}},"additionalProperties":false},"annotations":{"title":"process_sense","readOnlyHint":true,"destructiveHint":false,"idempotentHint":true,"openWorldHint":false}},{"name":"service_restart","description":"【变更类】重启指定 systemd 服务单元（systemctl restart），真实执行成功后自动以 systemctl is-active 复核服务状态。内置安全闭环：护栏风险裁决（核心服务自动升级为高危）、pendingMutationId + confirm=true 二次确认、溯源审计；默认 dry-run 不真实落盘","inputSchema":{"type":"object","properties":{"unit":{"type":"string","description":"systemd 服务单元名，如 nginx、crond、myapp.service"},"confirm":{"type":"boolean","description":"二次确认标志：首次调用返回风险裁决（REVIEW_PENDING），审阅后需同时携带 pendingMutationId 才会执行","default":false},"pendingMutationId":{"type":"string","description":"首次 REVIEW_PENDING 返回的待确认变更 id；confirm=true 时必须携带且与同一工具/参数匹配"}},"required":["unit"],"additionalProperties":false},"annotations":{"title":"service_restart","readOnlyHint":false,"destructiveHint":true,"idempotentHint":false,"openWorldHint":false}},{"name":"system_sense","description":"采集系统基线信息：内核版本(uname)、运行时长与负载(uptime)、内存使用(free)","inputSchema":{"type":"object","properties":{},"additionalProperties":false},"annotations":{"title":"system_sense","readOnlyHint":true,"destructiveHint":false,"idempotentHint":true,"openWorldHint":false}},{"name":"health_inspect","description":"主动巡检：只读体检磁盘/内存/负载/进程/端口/错误日志，输出健康评分与风险预警(不触发任何变更)","inputSchema":{"type":"object","properties":{},"additionalProperties":false},"annotations":{"title":"health_inspect","readOnlyHint":true,"destructiveHint":false,"idempotentHint":true,"openWorldHint":false}}]}}
{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":3,"result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"inspectId\":\"b11d4ca5-f808-4b6a-a06c-0628a15ad42b\",\"traceId\":\"c1737a64-0cda-4e60-9b1c-9f4af9b70329\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-07T05:14:32.500165070Z\",\"healthScore\":65,\"overall\":\"CRITICAL\",\"summary\":\"健康评分 65/100，总体状态 CRITICAL。需关注：系统负载(1分钟/核)=2.62 (load1=2.62, 核=1)(CRITICAL)；系统错误日志(近200条优先级<=err)=74(WARN)。\",\"findings\":[{\"category\":\"disk\",\"severity\":\"OK\",\"title\":\"磁盘使用率(最高分区 /boot)\",\"observed\":\"44%\",\"threshold\":\">=80% 告警 / >=90% 严重\",\"evidence\":\"/dev/vda2               983040   422788   560252  44% /boot\",\"suggestion\":\"磁盘容量充足，无需处理\"},{\"category\":\"memory\",\"severity\":\"OK\",\"title\":\"内存使用率\",\"observed\":\"38%\",\"threshold\":\">=85% 告警 / >=95% 严重\",\"evidence\":\"total=11827408 used=4534320 (KB)\",\"suggestion\":\"内存充足，无需处理\"},{\"category\":\"load\",\"severity\":\"CRITICAL\",\"title\":\"系统负载(1分钟/核)\",\"observed\":\"2.62 (load1=2.62, 核=1)\",\"threshold\":\">=1.0 告警 / >=2.0 严重\",\"evidence\":\"13:14:32 up 3 days, 17:28,  3 users,  load average: 2.62, 0.99, 0.64\\n\\n[output-audit] 完整 70 bytes 已落盘: logs/exec-output/73f79dae-cd1a-42f9-b4fb-95f8537bdd10-stdout.log\",\"suggestion\":\"定位高 CPU 进程(top/ps)，确认是否异常进程或突发流量；必要时限流或扩容\"},{\"category\":\"process\",\"severity\":\"OK\",\"title\":\"僵尸进程数\",\"observed\":\"0\",\"threshold\":\">=1 告警 / >=5 严重\",\"evidence\":\"检测到 0 个 Z 状态进程\",\"suggestion\":\"无僵尸进程\"},{\"category\":\"network\",\"severity\":\"OK\",\"title\":\"监听端口数\",\"observed\":\"11\",\"threshold\":\"仅供参考\",\"evidence\":\"当前共 11 个 TCP/UDP 监听套接字\",\"suggestion\":\"如需排查端口占用，可走主链路指令 ss -tlnp / lsof -i\"},{\"category\":\"log\",\"severity\":\"WARN\",\"title\":\"系统错误日志(近200条优先级<=err)\",\"observed\":\"74\",\"threshold\":\">=20 告警 / >=100 严重\",\"evidence\":\"匹配到 74 条错误级日志（近 5 分钟内 0 条）\",\"suggestion\":\"查看最近错误(journalctl -p 3 -xb)，结合知识库 runbook 定位故障源\"}],\"predictions\":[],\"sources\":[\"df -P\",\"free\",\"uptime + nproc\",\"ps -eo stat\",\"ss -H -tuln\",\"journalctl -p 3 -n 200 -o short-iso\"],\"elapsedMs\":195}"}],"structuredContent":{"inspectId":"b11d4ca5-f808-4b6a-a06c-0628a15ad42b","traceId":"c1737a64-0cda-4e60-9b1c-9f4af9b70329","timestamp":"2026-07-07T05:14:32.500165070Z","healthScore":65,"overall":"CRITICAL","summary":"健康评分 65/100，总体状态 CRITICAL。需关注：系统负载(1分钟/核)=2.62 (load1=2.62, 核=1)(CRITICAL)；系统错误日志(近200条优先级<=err)=74(WARN)。","findings":[{"category":"disk","severity":"OK","title":"磁盘使用率(最高分区 /boot)","observed":"44%","threshold":">=80% 告警 / >=90% 严重","evidence":"/dev/vda2               983040   422788   560252  44% /boot","suggestion":"磁盘容量充足，无需处理"},{"category":"memory","severity":"OK","title":"内存使用率","observed":"38%","threshold":">=85% 告警 / >=95% 严重","evidence":"total=11827408 used=4534320 (KB)","suggestion":"内存充足，无需处理"},{"category":"load","severity":"CRITICAL","title":"系统负载(1分钟/核)","observed":"2.62 (load1=2.62, 核=1)","threshold":">=1.0 告警 / >=2.0 严重","evidence":"13:14:32 up 3 days, 17:28,  3 users,  load average: 2.62, 0.99, 0.64\n\n[output-audit] 完整 70 bytes 已落盘: logs/exec-output/73f79dae-cd1a-42f9-b4fb-95f8537bdd10-stdout.log","suggestion":"定位高 CPU 进程(top/ps)，确认是否异常进程或突发流量；必要时限流或扩容"},{"category":"process","severity":"OK","title":"僵尸进程数","observed":"0","threshold":">=1 告警 / >=5 严重","evidence":"检测到 0 个 Z 状态进程","suggestion":"无僵尸进程"},{"category":"network","severity":"OK","title":"监听端口数","observed":"11","threshold":"仅供参考","evidence":"当前共 11 个 TCP/UDP 监听套接字","suggestion":"如需排查端口占用，可走主链路指令 ss -tlnp / lsof -i"},{"category":"log","severity":"WARN","title":"系统错误日志(近200条优先级<=err)","observed":"74","threshold":">=20 告警 / >=100 严重","evidence":"匹配到 74 条错误级日志（近 5 分钟内 0 条）","suggestion":"查看最近错误(journalctl -p 3 -xb)，结合知识库 runbook 定位故障源"}],"predictions":[],"sources":["df -P","free","uptime + nproc","ps -eo stat","ss -H -tuln","journalctl -p 3 -n 200 -o short-iso"],"elapsedMs":195},"isError":false}}
